      update m-tx to 0.63a which fixes FTBFS on hurd (Closes: #896518)
    - upstream-svn47477-ptexdir-fix-a-regression-for-discontinuous-kinsoku-t
      ptex regression fix
    - upstream-svn47506-typo
      typo in the changelog name
    -	upstream-svn47625-recover-to-give-tounicode-entries-for-ligatures
      search didn't work for ligatures
      https://tex.stackexchange.com/questions/430054/failing-search-for-words-with-ligatures-after-update
    - upstream-svn47626-ptexdir-More-strict-check-kanji-token
      inconsisten behavior of p-engines
  * add information about SDE in tex.man and etex.man (Closes: #897627)
  * use pkg-config as fallback for freetype configuration (Closes: #892446)

